ack." [More downplaying and minimisation, refers to Rob's writing by activi=
ty twice, but not to Rob as "author" ever, (likely non-inadvertent) omissio=
n of Rob's other significant professional engagements - eg, columnist at th=
e Boston Globe and TFP, lecturer at UTX and the Peterson Academy.]</span></=
p><p><span>(3) Richard's self-puffery</span></p><p><span>Richard in addendu=
