f hesitation to self-aggrandise; I suppose non-Ivies and not-Oxbridge?*]</s=
pan></p><p><span>(4) The respective authors' key accolades as stated by the=
mselves on their substack bios</span></p><p><span>Rob: Rob Henderson is the=
 bestselling author of "Troubled: A Memoir of Family, Foster Care, and Soci=
al Class." A veteran of the U.S. Air Force, he holds a B.S. from Yale and a=
