ege). [I recognise every single one of these accomplishments as legit ones.=
]</span></p><p><span>Richard: Richard Hanania is the President [very grand =
self-appointed title] of the Center for the Study of Partisanship and Ideol=
ogy [lots of words for a no-name org].</span></p><p><span>People, I think w=
e can see for ourselves the relative difference, and some obvious ick in wh=
at comes across as envy-driven covert strategies of diminishment and perhap=
s some hard riding-of-the-coattails. </span></p><p><span>*Not shading other=
